{
  "stem": "6195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, well, he come out of the sentry, from-- it's nice and warm inside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He will come out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, look, I haven't got much time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Are you coming or not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, you are out of your mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hope I see you back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, well, see you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was running through that Platz, I tell you, as though some-- something was pushing me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the sentry knocked-- when I ran through-- ran through there-- she knocked in the window.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where is the pass?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said-- here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, if you say something, I can't open it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's raining.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It will pull apart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he thought that I have it in my fist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had nothing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I walked in, and I saw Schubke on the door-- the name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I walked in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To my disappointment, Miller was sitting here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the [GERMAN], which means he dealt with the employment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very dangerous man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schubke wasn't, but he was an extremely dangerous man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even more dangerous was his dog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they wanted, they sent a dog at you, and you were chewed up to pieces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I nearly died when I walked in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knocked on the door, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they said [GERMAN], so Schubke said, who are you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you want?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I am [GERMAN], which is a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just wanted to draw your attention to the fact that a big mistake has occurred-- me and the mistakes, all the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, what mistake?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, look, I'm-- I was working at the [GERMAN], and somehow I'm not on the list.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
